                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-367-off1999 t18250915-367-cd2000"></join>, a watch, value 30 s.; a seal, value 8 s.; a key, value 4 s., and a ribbon, value 1 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-367-victim1854" type="victimName">
